en.title: FE Grows in New Zealand!
en.content:
REPORT SUBMITTED BY FE AUSTRALIAN COUNTRY LICENSEE VASU.

New Zealand Country Licensee Geoff & Josy Doyle took part in a health expo at Christchurch in New Zealand on 28th February and 01st March 2009, after relocating back to New Zealand from Australia. This was FE New Zealand's first public event and the local team was supported by PD Patricia Thava. The 2 day expo was well patronized by people interested in alternative medicine and FE's booths were no doubt a popular destination within the expo venue. Visitors were amazed by the instant results of demonstrations using FE's Quantum Science products. Several members have joined the FE network following the expo, with the appointment of a local stockiest in Christchurch under process. 

The Christchurch event was followed by another 2 days health expo at Cambridge, near Hamilton on the weekend of 04th & 05th March 2009. Several hundred people attended the expo and once again FE's booth was popular with patrons with many queuing up for demonstrations. Geoff & Josy, the New Zealand Country Licensees were joined by FE members from Christchurch and Australian Country Licensee, Vasu.
